name: Shalece Batchelor
coverLetter:
My Name is Shalece Batchelor, I am deeply passionate about the industry.  I have applied for my workers permit with O.L.C.C, I passed the test I am waiting to for my application to be processed. . I am a fast learner and I am willing to do whatever it takes to get the Job done. Ive been trimming for about 2 months, I can put out 2 pounds in a 7/8 hour shift. I am looking for full time year around work. I am from Utah, I am currently staying in Medford. But I am willing to travel wherever. I have my own car. I am very dependable. I always have a great attitude. Thank you for your time, I hope I work for you!
801-471-7879
